{"tid":866272,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝你比咗段咁特別既回憶我","createTime":"2018-10-17T17:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T18:04:49.000Z","uid":171297,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6bc0f5f9f3c23ccaa6907fc92ef0c0813ec970","tid":866272,"uid":171297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:23:13.000Z","msg":"令我過咗7年 都係忘記唔到你<br />\n其實我知道我留戀既<br />\n係過去同你相處既感覺<br />\n太快樂 快樂到冇人再比到相同既感覺我<br />\n但我真係迷惘<br />\n因為我分唔到係我太執著於過去既你<br />\n定係因為真係未有合適既人出現<br />\n所以我對你念念不忘<br />\n明明已經過去咗咁耐<br />\n有時一見返某啲野去到某個地點遇到相同既野<br />\n個腦總係會諗返起你<br />\n但其實我已經差唔多唔記得你把聲<br />\n望到你個樣會覺得陌生<br />\n與其話中意你不如話係中意過去果段回憶<br />\n或者係過去果段回憶入面既人<br />\n可能我只係太寂寞<br />\n但我每次一諗返起你 我個心就好痛好痛<br />\n我好想有日諗返起你係釋然 而唔係再痛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a39213ad121171aa04cb7cca26d696593791748","tid":866272,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"癲夠未？"},{"pid":"6fd321168ee9bdd4751f000ce9eac7e01c5a7a80","tid":866272,"uid":42079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:25:26.000Z","msg":"又係7年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64c855820f4ce93990b3d321d34445151ab920c","tid":866272,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post，就快8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢有好嘅生活，永遠唔好記起我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78aa4a0a79b02ffcfb93f0e88c21f1006961163b","tid":866272,"uid":171297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a39213ad121171aa04cb7cca26d696593791748","tid":866272,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"癲夠未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bea55a8c0194240bbb6e63d0c4ef872f